*<div id="function.mssql-get-last-message" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">mssql_get_last_message</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4, PHP 5, PECL odbtp &gt;= 1.1.1)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">mssql_get_last_message</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Returns the last message from the server</span></p>   </div>    <div id="function.mssql-get-last-message-refsynopsisdiv">   <div class="warning"><strong class="warning">Warning</strong>     <p class="para">  This function was <em class="emphasis">REMOVED</em> in PHP 7.0.0. </p> <p class="para">  Alternatives to this function include: </p>     <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link PDOStatement::errorInfo()}</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link sqlsrv_errors()}</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link odbc_errormsg()}</span></li>    </ul>   </div>  </div>   <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.mssql-get-last-message-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">    <span class="type">string</span> <span class="methodname"><strong>mssql_get_last_message</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam">void</span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    Gets the last message from the MS-SQL server   </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.mssql-get-last-message-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <p class="para">此函数没有参数。</p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.mssql-get-last-message-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    Returns last error message from server, or an empty string if     no error messages are returned from MSSQL.   </p>  </div>    <div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-function.mssql-get-last-message-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <p class="para">    <div class="example" id="example-1759">   